Text: RE email problem Cc Steve is set to unlimited space now He and his assistant or anyone else that may have it open will need to close out of his mailboxOutlook and reopen it in order for it to take effect CB Original Message From Pickering Mark Sent Thursday December AM To Behney Chris Cc Kean Steven J Subject email problem Chris Steves email was reset recently and the standard file size limit was reestablished This needs to be removed as Steve needs to ba able to use email and has many documents filed that he is not allowed to delete Thanks MRP

Market Data Contracts Cc PST Everyone We are in the process of creating new contracts with UBS for all Market Data realtime applications subscriptions and publications Attached is a comprehensive list of all contracts that will be renegotiated under the UBS name for use by the Gas and Power trading entities In order to leverage UBS significant discounts and avoid duplicate efforts Danielle Marcinkowski with Market Data will be the initial point of contact when inquiring about the addition or status of applications or publications I bring this to your attention because we understand that several groups have initiated discussions with the various vendors over the past few days If you have any questions please feel free to contact me at or Danielle at If you think something is missing from the list please bring it to our attention immediately Please pass this word around within your group as appropriate Regards Chris Behney
